## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the scope of the sources reviewed. Some sources may not reflect the most current economic conditions or account for recent policy changes aimed at addressing overfishing. Additionally, the complexity of global fishing industries means that the economic impacts can vary significantly by region, which may not be fully captured in this report. Further research and data collection are necessary to provide a more comprehensive analysis of the economic impacts of overfishing.